===========
Description
===========

This program uses OpenGL Shading Language to produce a water surface with floating leaves.

===========
Compilation
===========

"make" gives the program "glslRenderer"

"make clean" removes the intermediate files generated during compilation.

=====
Usage
=====

------------
Command Line
------------

./glslRenderer [w = 600] [h = w]

----------
Parameters
----------

w 		Window width. Default 600.

h		Window height. Default w.

==============
User Interface
==============

--------------
Key Operations
--------------

Esc/Q   Quit the program

V   	Use per-vertex render mode

F       Use per-fragment render mode

